telemetry.userPrompt: Build an interactive analytics dashboard for The Traitors Season 3 with episode-gated spoiler protection, player breakdowns, social game scores, deception tracking, and game statistics.
telemetry.researchPlan:
TOPIC: The Traitors US Season 3 Game Analytics
SOURCES: Wikipedia, Peacock Official Recaps (Ep 1-11), NBC Insider, Fandom Wiki
PLAYERS: 23 contestants with full stats
EPISODES: 11 game episodes + reunion
METRICS: Social game score, vote accuracy, shields, deceptions, alliances, eliminations
SPOILER SYSTEM: Episode gate (1-11) hides future events
SECTIONS: Overview, Players, Timeline, Deception, Alliances

contentAnalysis.readabilityNote: Interactive game analytics with spoiler-gated episode progression, player profiles, deception tracking, and social game scoring
